                                                                      SECTION 1
 
 
                                                                   INTRODUCTION
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
       _______       PURPOSE
 
 
       The enclosed tape includes all patches released against CP-6 supported
       products.  This tape has update packets and a full patch file so the
       customer can decide how he wants to maintain his own site's patches.  If
       you have no site-specific patches running at your site, then you might
       want to simply merge your own TIGR file into the full patch file and run
       with it.  If, on the other hand, you have already modified your patch
       file, you will probably want to add in the updates and run with those.
 
       The products and versions currently supported are as follows:
 
            Product           Version      Product            Version
            -------           -------      -------            -------
            OPERATING SYSTEM    E05        GMAP Assembler       B01*
            APL                 E00-       IDP                  B04*
            ARES-II             D02        I-D-S/II             C00
            BASIC               E01*       PL-6                 E03
            COBOL85             A06        ARGENT               A03
            COBOL-74            C00-       RPG-II               B04-
            ELECTRONIC MAIL     B06        Screen Editor 6Edit  A05
            FORTRAN-77          E03        SORT/MERGE           C00
            COMMON MATH LIBRARY E04        TEXT Processing      C03*
            C COMPILER          C03        DIGS (Graphics)      E00-
            ADAPT               B01-       Microcomp. Support   A02
            FORGE               B02        FPL                  E02
            CAP                 B01-       Micro FPL            A01-
            GCOS6 MOVE          A00        PC Terminal Facility A00-
            OSI Library Serv.   A01-       Utility Programs     E05
            OSI Remote FEP SW   E05        X.400                A01-
            TCP/IP & NFS        A02        Mirrored Disk        E05
 
       * Class II support,  - CLASS III SUPPORT
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
       SRB_PATCHES                      Purpose                             1-1
       
 
 
 
 
 
